data.description: Welcome home to your beautiful 4 sides brick ranch located in sought after Crystal Lake Golf and Country Club, a premier gated community.  Open concept plan with large vaulted family room, spacious kitchen with white cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, island, pantry and breakfast room.  Off the kitchen you will find a oversized keeping room with fireplace.  Also off the kitchen you will find the laundry room.  The main level also includes the owner's suite with trey ceilings and cozy fireplace.  Master bath boast dual vanities, jetted soaker tub and separate shower.  Also on the main level you will find 2 other bedrooms and a full bath.  Upstairs you will find the 4th bedroom and full bathroom.  This room is very large and can be used as a bonus room/flex space.  Home features luxury plantation shutters throughout.  This home sits on a half acre lot, flat and nicely landscaped with irrigation system.  3 car side entry garage.  Community features a lake, country club, golf course, pool, tennis courts and more!  Conveniently located to restaurants and shopping. Don't wait book your appointment today!
